data.description: Newly remodeled home boasts an array of upgrades. Step inside to discover the plush new carpeting and beautiful 24-inch tile floors. Fresh paint throughout the entire home gives it a pristine and modern look. The heart of this home is the stunning kitchen, featuring brand new quartz countertops and equipped with brand new stainless-steel appliances. Located in the picturesque community of Heartland, you'll enjoy all amenities including a resort style pool,  basketball and tennis courts, and walking trails. This is a must see! Foundation inspected with engineers report and transferable warranty.
